Module org.monarchinitiative.phenol.annotations
Package org.monarchinitiative.phenol.annotations.base.temporal

Interface AgeRange

All Superinterfaces:
TemporalInterval
public interface AgeRange extends TemporalInterval
A pair of Ages where the start() is before or equal to end().

AgeRange can be precise or imprecise based on the underlying start() and end().
